
flowchart TD
    A[Identify Hazards] --> B[Assess Risks]
    B --> C[Evaluate Significance]
    C --> D{Acceptable?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Monitor]
    D -->|No| F[Develop Controls]
    F --> G[Implement Controls]
    G --> H[Monitor Effectiveness]
    H --> I{Effective?}
    I -->|Yes| E
    I -->|No| J[Review Controls]
    J --> F

    style A fill:#FFF3CD
    style E fill:#D1ECF1
    style F fill:#F8D7DA
